List of cancer genes to compute dnds values.

cancer_genes_dnds.Rd

List of gene ids (HuGO format) developed from Martincorena et al. to compute dnds values.

data(cancer_genes_dnds)

Format

List of cancer genes to compute dnds values.

Examples

data(cancer_genes_dnds)
print(cancer_genes_dnds)
